  "sourceCode": "Employer Portal",
  "title": "Finance & Operations Executive",
  "description": "<p><strong>About Red Alpha</strong></p><p>Red Alpha is a next-generation cybersecurity talent and services company dedicated to developing top-tier cyber professionals and delivering impactful security solutions. We believe in growing talent from the ground up and providing real-world opportunities for individuals to thrive in the cybersecurity and tech industries.</p><p><strong>About the Role</strong></p><p>We’re a fast-growing global group of companies and need someone hands-on, sharp, and proactive to be part our Finance and Ops. From billing and payments to closing the books, you’ll be at the heart of the business.</p><p>No boring desk job here - if you like variety, ownership, and making a real impact, you’ll thrive.</p><p><strong>What You’ll Be Doing</strong></p><ul><li>Keep cash flowing: PO management, client invoicing, vendor payments, staff claims, and reconciliations</li><li>Work with our outsourced accountants to close the books and prepare financial reports</li><li>Solve problems, answer questions, and help teams get stuff done</li><li>Streamline processes, templates, and systems as we scale</li><li>Own and manage financial and operations docs and repositories</li><li>Support audit processes (don’t worry, we make it painless!)</li></ul><p><strong>What We’re Looking For</strong></p><ul><li>Diploma or Degree in Accounting, Finance, Business, or similar</li><li>1–3  years in finance/accounting/ops</li><li>Hands-on client billing experience is a must</li><li>Comfortable with partial or full finance operations</li><li>Strong grasp of P&L, Balance Sheet, and Cash Flow</li><li>Detail-oriented, organized, and love solving problems</li><li>Strong Excel skills; Xero experience is a bonus</li></ul><p><strong>Why You’ll Love Working Here</strong></p><ul><li>Real ownership - your work actually moves the business forward</li><li>Broad exposure across finance and ops in Singapore and the US</li><li>Learn fast, grow fast in a small, ambitious team</li><li>Clear path to senior finance & ops roles</li><li>No red tape - just a team that gets stuff doneFinance & Operations Executive</li></ul>",
